description: Absolutely stunning condo in the sought-after Terraces at Peachtree places you just minutes from Buckhead, Midtown, and Downtown Atlanta! Inside, you’ll find modern LVP flooring, fresh paint. Enjoy your own private balcony with tranquil, tree-lined views plus the convenience of a deeded, covered parking spot, this is a charming unit.   The community offers resort-style amenities including a sparkling pool, fitness center, grilling stations, clubroom, and lush outdoor spaces; perfect for entertaining or relaxing.  Step outside and experience one of Atlanta’s most vibrant neighborhoods. Walk to the Atlanta BeltLine Northside Trail, play a round at Bobby Jones Golf Course, or take in a match at the Bitsy Grant Tennis Center. Grocery stores, top-tier dining, boutique shopping, and cultural attractions like the High Museum of Art and Fox Theatre are all within easy reach.  This is the lifestyle you’ve been waiting for stylish, convenient, and move-in ready. Schedule your showing today!
